text: The black-striped frog, black-spotted frog, black-sided wood frog, Sapgreen Stream frog, Mengla frog, dark-sided frog or Hekou frog (Sylvirana nigrovittata) is a frog from India, Nepal, Bangladesh, China,Vietnam, Laos and Thailand. It can live as high as 1100 meters above sea level. ==References== Category:Frogs of Asia
title: Sylvirana nigrovittata
